#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Google Cloud Functions (Serverless) with Quarkus REST, Undertow, or Reactive Routes"
msgstr "Google Cloud Functions (sem servidor) com Quarkus REST, Undertow ou Reactive Routes"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"This extension's backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">preview</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"A compatibilidade com versões anteriores e a presença desta extensão no ecossistema não são garantidas\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">visualização</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-google-cloud-functions-http` extension allows you to write microservices with Quarkus REST (Jakarta REST),\n"
"Undertow (Servlet), Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP], and make these microservices deployable to the Google Cloud Functions runtime."
msgstr "A extensão `quarkus-google-cloud-functions-http` permite que você desenvolva microsserviços com Quarkus REST (Jakarta REST), Undertow (Servlet), Reactive Routes ou xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] e torne esses microsserviços implantáveis no ambiente de execução do Google Cloud Functions."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "One Google Cloud Functions deployment can represent any number of Jakarta REST, Servlet, Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] endpoints."
msgstr "Uma implantação do Google Cloud Functions pode representar qualquer número de pontos de extremidade xref:funqy-http.adoc[HTTP] do Jakarta REST, Servlet, Reactive Routes ou xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy] ."

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "Pré-requisitos"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://cloud.google.com/[A Google Cloud Account]. Free accounts work."
msgstr "link:https://cloud.google.com/[Uma conta do Google Cloud] . As contas gratuitas são suficientes."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://cloud.google.com/sdk[Cloud SDK CLI Installed]"
msgstr "link:https://cloud.google.com/sdk[CLI do Cloud SDK instalada]"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Solution"
msgstr "Solução"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide walks you through generating a sample project followed by creating three HTTP endpoints\n"
"written with Jakarta REST APIs, Servlet APIs, Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] APIs. Once built, you will be able to deploy\n"
"the project to Google Cloud."
msgstr "Este guia o orienta na geração de um projeto de exemplo, seguida pela criação de três endpoints HTTP escritos com as APIs REST do Jakarta, as APIs Servlet, o Reactive Routes ou as APIs xref:funqy-http.adoc[HTTP do Funqy] . Após a criação, o senhor poderá implantar o projeto no Google Cloud."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you don't want to follow all these steps, you can go right to the completed example."
msgstr "Caso não queira seguir todas essas etapas, você pode ir diretamente para o exemplo completo."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Clone the Git repository: `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}`, or download an {quickstarts-archive-url}[archive]."
msgstr "Clone o repositório Git: `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}` , ou baixe um {quickstarts-archive-url}[arquivo]."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The solution is located in the `google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart` link:{quickstarts-tree-url}/google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart[directory]."
msgstr "A solução está localizada no link:{quickstarts-tree-url}/google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart[diretório] `google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart` ."

